org.drip.spaces.graph

Class SinglyLinkedNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.spaces.graph.SinglyLinkedNode

  • public class SinglyLinkedNode
extends java.lang.Object
    SinglyLinkedNode implements the Node behind a Singly Linked List. The References are: 1) Donald Knuth (1973): The Art of Computer Programming, Addison-Wesley. 2) Oracle (2018): LinkedList (Java Platform SE 7), https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/LinkedList.html. 3) Wikipedia (2018a): Linked List https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linked_list. 4) Wikipedia (2018b): Doubly Linked List https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doubly_linked_list. 5) Wikipedia (2018c): Linked Data Structure, https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linked_data_structure.

    Lakshmi Krishnamurthy
